Text: Cigars Avo docCigar Night at the Club Its not too late to take advantage of this rare opportunity to meet Avo A few places and a few cigars remain Meet and smoke with Avo Uvezian who has prepared a special vertical tasting and discussion of three of his most famous cigars Taste rare fine single malt Scotch Balvenie year old aged in port wood Bowmore year old Bowmore Darkest Glenlivet French Oak Finish Aberlour aBunadh very rare Sip rare Scotch smoke fine cigars and listen to the wisdom of Avo Also here to answer your questions Mr Sam Russell Director of Marketing and Product Development Davidoff USA Mr Kris Miller Territory Manager for Davidoff USA and Mr Jeffrey Stone Davidoff Appointed Merchant Tuesday October PM Per Person
